{"tid":1423841,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"可唔可以唔好再推啲叫人衝嘅post","createTime":"2019-08-06T14:59:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T00:27:53.000Z","uid":150848,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0f5abed70d980f0383ba3d228b0c00a8d2a1c2e0","tid":1423841,"uid":150848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:59:41.000Z","msg":"而家去到8月，好明顯政府手段只會越黎越硬，但係我哋實質攞到啲咩，大家冷靜諗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家再衝，只會令到<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">更多兄弟送頭</span></span>，叫人送頭係咩心態，政府而家擺明<span style=\"color: red;\">想你送頭</span>，用媒體每日抹黑我哋個運動。我哋而家根本係要<span style=\"color: red;\">每日</span>用文宣核單，反擊，再用和理非方法坑爭，比勇武休息。<br />\n<br />\n我好多謝勇武擋子彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但坦唔係咁做，喺唔需要擋子彈嘅時候擋哂，只會喺真正要打嘅時候冇哂我哋嘅盾<br />\n<br />\n我知好多手足都好嬲，因為每次都有好多人比人拉咗，但我想講正正因為咁更加要沉住道氣，只要手足<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一日未被忘記，呢個運動同佢哋都唔會完</span></span>，而家上前線只會令我哋冇哂勇武建立返黎嘅優勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勇武難求，休養生息</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">養兵千日，用在一時</span></span>"},{"pid":"39041cffe6b8c1f0b528eef8774825a78ad95c0a","tid":1423841,"uid":150848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:00:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"787d67df79b2b793804d46c3427f283865c1e355","tid":1423841,"uid":150848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:01:13.000Z","msg":"push push push"},{"pid":"0123d887428760f0618267271e815c02c4911712","tid":1423841,"uid":150848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:04:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"26065777f739aa2da026f2b1206ff78bf68485b9","tid":1423841,"uid":150848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:04:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"